Title: Nothing Important Happened Today II (2)
Plot: Doggett catches up with Shannon McMahon, the woman who the EPA official picked up. She claims to be a super solider and that the people she has killed were poisoning the water supply, and she wants Doggett to expose the truth.
GuestStars: Lucy Lawless, Adam Baldwin, Ryan Cutrona, Ben Reed, Victoria Gallegos, Kevin E. West, Wyatt Smith, Jeff Austin
